{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "8ab59645-4423-45e7-b90c-5ad3826d8d25", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8ab59645-4423-45e7-b90c-5ad3826d8d25@3.pkg/1772597527757/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597528312", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8ab59645-4423-45e7-b90c-5ad3826d8d25@3.pkg/1772597527757/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597528312"}, "identifier": "8ab59645-4423-45e7-b90c-5ad3826d8d25", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>对于社会生活中存在的不平等现象，需要每个公民把平等原则落实到日常的生活、学习和工作中，要敢于抵制不平等行为。某招聘网站的招聘要求是就业歧视的表现，侵害了求职者的合法权益，对于求职者要据理力争，必要情况下可诉诸法律，因此，B、C、D为正确选项，A为错误选项，选A。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>某招聘网站上，一些企业负责人明确要求只招已婚已育女性，不招录“本科双非”(非“双一流”建设高校)毕业的学生，不招录农村户口的人，这些看似简单的招聘要求隐含着各种就业歧视。对此认识错误的是( &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)</p>\n", "title": "某招聘网站上，一些企业负责人明确要求只招已婚已育女性，不招录“本科双非”(非“双一流”建设高校)毕业的学生，不招录农村户口的人，这些看似简单的招聘要求隐含着各种就业歧视。对此认识错误的是(    )", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/8ab59645-4423-45e7-b90c-5ad3826d8d25@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754837965802", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "res